dc:description: Yellow glass with streaky green collar.  Intact.  Milky weathering.  Bubbly.  Blowing spirals.  Sandy and black impurities.  Flask.  Rim outsplayed horizontally and folded upward and inward.  Neck tall and cylindrical with constriction at base.  Oval body with greatest diameter below center.  On shoulder a trailed on collar of streaky green drawn glass, on which are seven vertical pinched-out flaps.  Seven pinched slants on body.  Concave base.  No pontil mark.
